  ID: MenAtArms
  Name: Anselm
  Icon: {fileID: -2105629146, guid: d556a7f542c7d03429c5a535ce31a084, type: 3}
  Description: 'Wound: A jagged gash across the scalp from a falling stone, skull
    cracked, eyes fluttering.


    Story: Brother Anselm, a Hospitaller scribe no
    older than twenty, never trained for war. His hands, ink-stained and trembling,
    clutch at nothing as he mutters half-remembered prayers. Blood fills his mouth
    as he whispers that he only wanted to preserve holy texts, not die with a sword
    overhead.



    Required bandages to heal: 3'
